    Class Description
    AbstractBase40<E extends AbstractBase40<E>>
    AbstractBase40 represents an abstract base class for 64bit non-negative base-40 values.

    AbstractLightweightBase40 represents an abstract base class for 64bit non-negative base-40 values.
    Base40
    Base40 represents a 64bit non-negative base-40 value.
    Base40Converter
    Base40Converter converts Base40 to and from Java long.
    CharacterSet
    A Base40 character set is used to convert Base-40 values to and from String.

    Helper class allows creating pseudo-enumerations out of Enum40 instances.
    EnumLongConverter<E extends Enum<E>>
    EnumLongConverter implements a LongConverter for some enum type.

    Path represents a 64bit non-negative base-40 "path".
